data.description: This 2016 build has been Upgraded and Remodeled! Now with an open floor plan, it's Light and Bright! New upgraded large tile throughout the home. This beautiful home has a new island in the kitchen, granite countertops, new custom cabinetry-pantry. Generous Master Bedroom upstairs, has a large En Suite Bathroom with a Roman Soaking Tub for Relaxing after a long day with a separate shower. 3 additional bedrooms and a guest bathroom with dual sinks, Washer and Dryer also located upstairs for maximum convenience and completes this upstairs living space. A half bath located on the main level. Large yard, backyard is mostly fenced in with plenty of roam for an Oasis & pool. Lots of new Coconut Palms have been planted to give you that Florida feel! 3 Car garage, 5+ car driveway. 3+ pets, NO HOA.
